724493f-a.title: Manhattan: Houston Street (West - Mercer Street
724493f-a.text:
Houston Street, west from and including site of No. 15-17 West Houston
Street at the S.E. corner of Mercer Street.
Pebruary 21, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

724494f-a.title: Manhattan: Houston Street (West - Mercer Street
724494f-a.text:
20, 22, 26 West Houston Street, at and adjoining the N.W. corner of
Mercer Street. No. 22 is the little house with dormer windows,
sandwiched in between two iron-fronted loft buildings of the
type that began to be built in the 1870's.
February 21, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

724495f-a.title: Manhattan: Houston Street (West - Mercer Street
724495f-a.text:
Houston Street, south side, west from and including Mercer Street
(the first street parallel to and west of Broadway), shortly
before the razing of the south side of Houston Street.
September 19, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
